/* Table: "MD_Mall2Entity" */

create table "MD_Mall2Entity"
(
"Mall2EntityID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"MallID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"MallCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"EntityID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"EntityCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_MD_MALL2ENTITY primary key ("Mall2EntityID")
);

comment on column "MD_Mall2Entity"."EntityID" is

comment on column "MD_Mall2Entity"."Enable" is
'1: 有效
0：无效';
